Cell["\<\
I hereby formally declare that we have written the submitted term paper \
entirely by ourselves without anyone else\[CloseCurlyQuote]s assistance. \
Wherever we have drawn on literature or other sources, either in direct \
quotes or in paraphrasing such material, we have given the reference to the \
original author or authors and to the source where it appeared. We are aware \
that the use of quotations, or close paraphrasing, from books, magazines, \
newspapers, the internet, or other sources, which are not marked as such, \
will be considered an attempt at deception, and that the term paper will be \
graded with a fail. We are aware of the fact, that the use of Large Language \
Models (LLM) like ChatGPT or others without a quotation will be graded with a \
fail, too.\
\>", "Text",
