   3.9914548937959766`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"4feb689e-927e-4a17-ae1e-\
d3742171e30e"],

Cell["\<\
Instead of fixing 18, the total S can be any value - this is the sweep of \
Section 6. Two rules generalize the case S = 18:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.6551323318137064`*^9, 3.655132346618133*^9}, {
   3.6558834788297663`*^9, 3.655883482105772*^9}, {3.655883581805547*^9, 
